                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   {
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    "content": "Gotcha. I bet when we fixed the infinite loop issue we introduced this one. Here are two thoughts. 1. We should id all items to be tokenized, and then replace them all with tokens rather than id - token - id - token. 2. We should be sure we exclude our token from the pattern looking for items to tokenize. What do you think? Finally, a question about the previous tests. you said we aren't keeping inline comments inline - why not?",
